TestNG -- unit test framework
TDD --Test Driven Development

Purpose of TestNG? desing test cases in a systematic way
--it will generate good html reports
-- gives different annotations
-- we can define prioritiies like which function to execute first
-- we can define dependencies
-- grouping
--data provider feature
it is open source, free
available in the form of JAR files
-- it is also called java unit testing framework

how to install?
https://dl.bintray.com/testng-team/testng-eclipse-release/6.14.3/